1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:02,110
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:02,170 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:04,980
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:10,180 --> 00:00:11,320
(Episode 77)

5
00:00:12,050 --> 00:00:13,080
Here...

6
00:00:14,690 --> 00:00:15,820
This pearl...

7
00:00:16,790 --> 00:00:19,060
will prove
that Oh Jung Ran committed murder.

8
00:00:28,130 --> 00:00:30,030
The blood on this...

9
00:00:30,370 --> 00:00:31,940
most likely belongs
to the killer too.

10
00:00:32,370 --> 00:00:33,370
So that's why...

11
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:37,680
That's why...

12
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:41,150
Myung Hui was holding onto this
until the very end.

13
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:45,350
Myung Hui,

14
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:49,420
I'm sorry...

15
00:00:51,460 --> 00:00:52,460
it took me so long.

16
00:00:54,890 --> 00:00:57,600
Dad, are you watching?

17
00:00:58,200 --> 00:01:03,130
The pearl in red that you protected
is finally where it belongs.

18
00:01:14,850 --> 00:01:18,150
How will you use this evidence?

19
00:01:19,150 --> 00:01:22,620
I'm going to hold a press conference
and reveal Oh Jung Ran's murder.

20
00:01:23,490 --> 00:01:24,990
The case involving
her boss at Munhwadang...

21
00:01:24,990 --> 00:01:26,390
was dropped
due to a lack of evidence.

22
00:01:26,930 --> 00:01:29,460
But I'm a witness in this case
and the evidence is solid,

23
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:31,600
so she won't be able to bury it.

24
00:01:32,230 --> 00:01:33,870
A legal conviction
might be difficult,

25
00:01:34,630 --> 00:01:36,470
but she'll be branded a murderer.

26
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:38,800
Park Tae Ho and Park Hyun Jun...

27
00:01:39,070 --> 00:01:40,540
will abandon Oh Jung Ran.

28
00:01:41,740 --> 00:01:45,240
I'll make sure she's shut out
of the Adele Group she coveted so much.

29
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:49,580
She's the kind of person
who'd kill to have it all.

30
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:52,420
If she loses everything
because of her greed,

31
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,890
her life will become a nightmare.

32
00:01:56,420 --> 00:01:57,760
If you hold a press conference,

33
00:01:58,760 --> 00:02:00,430
you'll have to reveal
that Kim Myung Hui is dead...

34
00:02:01,630 --> 00:02:05,600
and that you're
actually Kim Dan Hui.

35
00:02:06,730 --> 00:02:09,670
That's been my plan for seven years.

36
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:14,510
It'll be a difficult conversation
with Min Jun,

37
00:02:15,710 --> 00:02:18,910
but it's time I dealt
with my own unfinished business.

38
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,880
Then we need to do a DNA test first.

39
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:28,250
We need to prove the blood
on the pearl is Oh Jung Ran's.

40
00:02:28,690 --> 00:02:31,920
For the test,
we'll need a strand of her hair.

41
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,360
Right. I'll go get it right now.

42
00:02:39,430 --> 00:02:42,330
If it were up to me,
I wouldn't let you go.

43
00:02:42,530 --> 00:02:45,040
Park Tae Ho will be
on your case again.

44
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,170
She's right.

45
00:02:46,670 --> 00:02:48,970
Chairman Park will continue
to be suspicious.

46
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:50,810
Are you sure you'll be okay?

47
00:02:51,010 --> 00:02:54,050
I have no reason to be afraid
of his suspicions anymore.

48
00:02:54,310 --> 00:02:58,620
In fact, I'm going to make him
even more suspicious.

49
00:03:06,420 --> 00:03:08,630
Hyun Jun's working late.

50
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:11,330
He must be busy preparing
for the vice president position.

51
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,900
Just tell him to end things
with Chloe already.

52
00:03:16,270 --> 00:03:19,200
- Where's Kim Myung Hui?
- I'll check the annex.

53
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,540
Leave her.

54
00:03:21,510 --> 00:03:23,540
She's a criminal
who was banished to the annex.

55
00:03:23,540 --> 00:03:25,080
Who cares if she eats or not?

56
00:03:35,550 --> 00:03:36,590
Mrs. Ok,

57
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:39,860
from now on,
I won't be dining with the chairman.

58
00:03:40,530 --> 00:03:42,960
- What?
- What do you think you're doing?

59
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:46,630
You banished me to the annex
because you don't trust me.

60
00:03:47,170 --> 00:03:51,200
How do you know
I won't poison you during dinner?

61
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:55,440
Exactly. Her eyes are full of venom.

62
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,510
She should be kicked...

63
00:03:57,510 --> 00:03:59,140
out of the house,
not just sent to the annex.

64
00:03:59,640 --> 00:04:01,680
- Sit down now!
- No.

65
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:07,090
Have your meal with Jung Ran,
the one you trust and cherish.

66
00:04:08,190 --> 00:04:10,420
Wait. Did you
just speak casually to me?

67
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:15,860
Oh Jung Ran. Your days sitting
in that chair are numbered.

68
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:19,930
Kim Myung Hui!

69
00:04:46,860 --> 00:04:49,760
You say
I'm unfairly suspicious of you,

70
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,630
but the evidence is this clear.

71
00:04:52,730 --> 00:04:54,700
- Evidence?
- That's right.

72
00:04:55,070 --> 00:04:57,540
Evidence that you went
to Eunhwa Trading.

73
00:04:57,640 --> 00:05:01,010
Evidence that you conspired
with Chloe to report me.

74
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:04,810
You knew about Park Cheol Su,
Eunhwa Trading, and...

75
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,450
You mean evidence
that I know about your wrongdoings.

76
00:05:08,650 --> 00:05:09,710
Seven years ago,

77
00:05:10,820 --> 00:05:11,920
the CEO of Temi Bio,

78
00:05:12,550 --> 00:05:14,120
Baek Jun Gi,

79
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:16,650
was murdered
in a staged car accident.

80
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:19,220
Yes, I know about that.

81
00:05:21,430 --> 00:05:25,400
Oh Jung Ran told me about it
when she ordered me to leave you.

82
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:30,000
But instead,
I chose to stand by your side.

83
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:32,570
Exactly.

84
00:05:32,870 --> 00:05:35,270
- Because you had to use me.
- No.

85
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,340
Because you...

86
00:05:37,980 --> 00:05:39,910
are Min Jun's father.

87
00:05:42,910 --> 00:05:46,620
It wasn't easy to turn a blind eye
to your crime.

88
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:51,160
Still, I saved you from Oh Jung Ran,

89
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:53,730
and for Min Jun's sake,

90
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,930
I wanted to be your perfect wife.

91
00:05:58,830 --> 00:05:59,830
Then...

92
00:06:00,630 --> 00:06:02,100
Then what about Chloe?

93
00:06:02,170 --> 00:06:05,500
Oh Jung Ran was the one
who told Chloe about Park Cheol Su.

94
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,870
She must've told Chloe
to dig up dirt on you.

95
00:06:08,170 --> 00:06:09,340
Chloe found Eunhwa Trading...

96
00:06:09,410 --> 00:06:11,480
without knowing what happened
seven years ago,

97
00:06:11,640 --> 00:06:15,050
so I stopped her
before she could find out.

98
00:06:16,210 --> 00:06:17,250
No.

99
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,620
I won't fall for your lies anymore.

100
00:06:20,750 --> 00:06:22,450
I've explained everything.

101
00:06:23,650 --> 00:06:27,260
Whether I'm lying
or telling the truth...

102
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:29,890
is for you to judge.

103
00:06:52,780 --> 00:06:53,790
Park Tae Ho.

104
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:56,850
You'll be tormented,
torn between lies and the truth.

105
00:06:57,420 --> 00:07:00,290
You won't know who to trust
and will be suspicious of everyone.

106
00:07:01,360 --> 00:07:05,100
That endless suspicion
will be another prison for you.

107
00:07:11,370 --> 00:07:12,840
What did you two talk about?

108
00:07:13,140 --> 00:07:14,170
What's wrong?

109
00:07:14,910 --> 00:07:17,580
Afraid I might've told him
your son's secret?

110
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:23,210
Didn't I tell you I'd ruin
your son's life if you talked?

111
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:26,550
You don't have to be so scared.

112
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:30,120
I have plenty of ways
to deal with you...

113
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,820
without using your son's secret.

114
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,230
Stubbornly proud until the end.

115
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:46,400
Now that Park Tae Ho is
suspicious of Kim Myung Hui,

116
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:48,740
this is my chance to strike.

117
00:07:49,240 --> 00:07:50,440
This is my opportunity...

118
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:54,810
to prove myself
as president of the bio division.

119
00:08:02,790 --> 00:08:04,520
Gosh, that's good.

120
00:08:05,620 --> 00:08:06,820
So refreshing.

121
00:08:08,460 --> 00:08:10,700
Don't tell me
you're feeling so good...

122
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,130
because you kicked Chloe out,
are you?

123
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,000
Why are you bringing that up?

124
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:18,070
I'm working this hard
for Hyun Jun's sake.

125
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:20,440
What does washing your hair
have to do with Hyun Jun?

126
00:08:20,710 --> 00:08:22,910
I tested the product myself
so I can be...

127
00:08:22,970 --> 00:08:24,980
a better president
of the bio division.

128
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:27,280
So, do you like it?

129
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:33,620
I washed my hair
with the ionized water,

130
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:35,050
and this thing is a miracle.

131
00:08:35,420 --> 00:08:39,690
You just switch from alkaline mode
to this one to finish up.

132
00:08:40,020 --> 00:08:43,160
All the stress from Kim Myung Hui
and Butler Ok...

133
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:44,400
left my scalp irritated,

134
00:08:44,400 --> 00:08:45,800
but now it feels refreshed
and clean.

135
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:48,830
Your hair does look better.

136
00:08:49,530 --> 00:08:52,340
If it's that good,
our Hyun Jun should try it.

137
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:55,240
I told you not to say
"our Hyun Jun."

138
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:58,040
Darn it, watch your mouth.

139
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:06,780
Our Hyun Jun must be under
a lot of stress too.

140
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:13,860
(Bion Tech)

141
00:09:18,900 --> 00:09:20,730
There's already some in the jug.

142
00:10:11,950 --> 00:10:14,690
Why did you come in person?
I said I'd send it with Yoon Jung.

143
00:10:14,890 --> 00:10:16,790
I was worried about you.

144
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:19,220
Didn't Chairman Park
give you a hard time?

145
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:24,030
I'm sure he's having
just as hard a time.

146
00:10:25,330 --> 00:10:26,930
I fanned his suspicions...

147
00:10:26,930 --> 00:10:28,600
so he won't be able to trust
Oh Jung Ran either.

148
00:10:29,270 --> 00:10:32,070
I told him you have nothing
to do with this,

149
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:34,140
so you should react the same way.

150
00:10:34,710 --> 00:10:37,040
Yes, for now I've told him...

151
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:39,710
that Oh Jung Ran sent me
to Eunhwa Trading.

152
00:10:40,410 --> 00:10:42,710
Good. And this.

153
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:48,220
I've gathered everything needed
for the DNA test.

154
00:10:48,850 --> 00:10:50,890
Okay, I'll request it right away.

155
00:10:51,220 --> 00:10:53,960
You should get back inside
before anyone gets suspicious.

156
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,360
Okay. Be careful.

157
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:12,410
Those two...

158
00:11:14,010 --> 00:11:15,010
But why?

159
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,060
Yu Na.

160
00:11:26,590 --> 00:11:28,090
Can I ask you something?

161
00:11:28,230 --> 00:11:31,460
Honey, please.
Can't you ask her after we eat?

162
00:11:31,530 --> 00:11:33,500
You're dying to know too.

163
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:37,130
I'm not the only one wondering
how she got the lawsuit dropped...

164
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,570
and got her job back.

165
00:11:41,410 --> 00:11:45,080
I got Chairman Park released
from police custody.

166
00:11:45,910 --> 00:11:48,180
- What?
- How did you manage that?

167
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:51,520
Your daughter is more capable
than you think.

168
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,990
I'm in the same boat
as Chairman Park now,

169
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:57,150
and things are only going
to get better for me.

170
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:58,660
Goodness.

171
00:11:58,690 --> 00:12:01,160
Do you really have to be
in the same boat as him?

172
00:12:01,230 --> 00:12:03,130
Tell me about it.

173
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:06,400
How can you trust a man
who even made a bomb?

174
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:09,570
Didn't you hear me?
I got him out of police custody.

175
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,240
The bomb allegation...

176
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,740
- isn't true.
- But still...

177
00:12:15,810 --> 00:12:17,780
You should cut ties
with that family.

178
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,040
What are you talking about?

179
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:21,080
That's a family we need to stay
on good terms with.

180
00:12:21,080 --> 00:12:22,980
You're not still trying...

181
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:26,180
to marry Park Min Jun, are you?

182
00:12:26,180 --> 00:12:27,990
Honey, come on.

183
00:12:28,290 --> 00:12:30,920
She'd have to be out of her mind
to still think that.

184
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:35,230
Just you wait. I have a plan.

185
00:12:35,730 --> 00:12:37,760
- Oh dear.
- What?

186
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:43,570
I mean, that girl.
Honestly, I can't...

187
00:12:44,140 --> 00:12:47,200
Can you believe this
from our one and only daughter?

188
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:51,680
How can she be such a headache?
She's a real handful.

189
00:12:51,740 --> 00:12:53,310
You're telling me.

190
00:12:53,510 --> 00:12:56,150
Some "precious child"
she turned out to be.

191
00:12:56,150 --> 00:12:57,820
No kidding.

192
00:12:58,820 --> 00:12:59,850
Honestly.

193
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:02,820
So, did you send it for analysis?

194
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:05,090
Yes, we should have...

195
00:13:05,090 --> 00:13:06,660
- the results tomorrow.
- Right.

196
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,360
For President Kim Myung Hui,

197
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,630
this will be a perfect opportunity
to get rid of Oh Jung Ran.

198
00:13:13,160 --> 00:13:15,470
Kim Dan Hui can finally live
as her true self.

199
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:21,010
You also need to go back
to being Jin Ju soon.

200
00:13:25,110 --> 00:13:26,210
I really am...

201
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:29,080
a troublesome daughter, aren't I?

202
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:32,550
You are.

203
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:37,890
I finally understand why people say
children make you age.

204
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:42,260
It was the same
when our Chloe went missing.

205
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:50,970
The truth is,

206
00:13:51,770 --> 00:13:53,970
I'm afraid I might fail
to protect you too.

207
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:59,240
Even at my age,
it scares me sometimes.

208
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:08,690
From seven years ago until now,

209
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,820
you've always protected me.

210
00:14:13,660 --> 00:14:17,160
James, you've been both my rock...

211
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,230
and a father to me.

212
00:14:22,470 --> 00:14:23,470
That's right.

213
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,970
And you're my daughter.

214
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,840
Yes, Dad.

215
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:31,410
So please cheer up.

216
00:14:31,910 --> 00:14:32,940
Got it.

217
00:14:36,510 --> 00:14:37,550
It seems President Kim...

218
00:14:37,550 --> 00:14:40,350
is putting pressure on Park Tae Ho
in her own way.

219
00:14:41,950 --> 00:14:44,620
Now it's our turn.

220
00:14:44,690 --> 00:14:47,660
I've already got something prepared.

221
00:14:56,370 --> 00:14:57,840
(Adele)

222
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:01,740
What, a formal notice?

223
00:15:01,910 --> 00:15:04,170
Yes. JKL Partners sent
a formal notice stating...

224
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:06,440
that they're filing a lawsuit
to recover the penalty fee.

225
00:15:06,910 --> 00:15:09,510
They're claiming a penalty
of 100 million dollars.

226
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:13,320
Who do they think they're suing?

227
00:15:14,020 --> 00:15:16,320
- Get the legal team in here now.
- Yes, sir.

228
00:15:20,490 --> 00:15:24,660
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

229
00:15:27,500 --> 00:15:30,400
Father, you must have been
quite surprised.

230
00:15:30,970 --> 00:15:34,770
My father said he was going to sue,
so I rushed him over.

231
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:37,610
We should settle this
before it gets to court.

232
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:39,240
Chairman Park.

233
00:15:39,480 --> 00:15:42,150
We at JKL Partners consider
our children's marriage...

234
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:44,520
to be part
of our joint venture agreement.

235
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:45,780
And yet,

236
00:15:46,320 --> 00:15:49,150
you threw my daughter out
in a most unjust way.

237
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:50,950
If you want to dissolve
this marriage,

238
00:15:50,950 --> 00:15:54,460
then cancel the joint venture
and pay the penalty fee.

239
00:15:56,030 --> 00:15:57,590
After everything
you've put me through,

240
00:15:58,530 --> 00:16:00,660
framing me and turning me in,

241
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:03,170
now you're demanding a penalty fee?

242
00:16:03,830 --> 00:16:05,900
You're the one
who should be paying it!

243
00:16:06,270 --> 00:16:09,570
Don't just stand there.
Call the legal team!

244
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:10,570
Yes, sir.

245
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:19,420
Fine.
Let's get our lawyers involved.

246
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:22,720
We'll settle this in court.

247
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:23,920
Then I'll have...

248
00:16:24,820 --> 00:16:29,490
to testify about Park Cheol Su
and Eunhwa Trading, won't I?

249
00:16:29,860 --> 00:16:30,860
What?

250
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:34,100
What are you going
to tell the court?

251
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:35,700
And if we end up in court,

252
00:16:35,770 --> 00:16:40,100
I'll have to explain that so-called
memory loss of mine too.

253
00:16:40,670 --> 00:16:45,610
I should probably try to remember
what happened at the warehouse.

254
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:51,180
I knew it.
You never lost your memory.

255
00:16:51,480 --> 00:16:55,520
I really wish
I hadn't lost my memory.

256
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:00,460
Well, we'll be on our way.

257
00:17:00,690 --> 00:17:03,260
We'll be busy preparing
for the lawsuit.

258
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:05,230
- Let's go, Dad.
- Sure.

259
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
Wait.

260
00:17:10,070 --> 00:17:12,240
Let me ask you one last thing.

261
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:17,570
Who told you to find Park Cheol Su
and turn him in?

262
00:17:18,180 --> 00:17:19,840
Was it Kim Myung Hui...

263
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:21,950
or Oh Jung Ran?

264
00:17:23,380 --> 00:17:26,420
I believe I already told you.

265
00:17:26,750 --> 00:17:28,350
You just didn't believe me.

266
00:17:29,620 --> 00:17:30,620
Then...

267
00:17:31,190 --> 00:17:32,860
(Chairman Park Tae Ho)

268
00:17:36,760 --> 00:17:39,030
She already told me?

269
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:43,130
Oh Jung Ran was behind this
after all?

270
00:17:43,630 --> 00:17:45,970
What the... Darn it!

271
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:48,840
Who the heck am I supposed to trust?

272
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:54,710
If Park Cheol Su and Eunhwa Trading
are brought up in court,

273
00:17:54,780 --> 00:17:56,210
things will get complicated.

274
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:58,350
Plus, if her memory is fine...

275
00:17:59,550 --> 00:18:02,250
and she brings up the warehouse incident,
I'm in big trouble.

276
00:18:03,690 --> 00:18:04,990
How do I clean this up?

277
00:18:06,890 --> 00:18:07,930
Darn it.

278
00:18:10,490 --> 00:18:12,030
- She completely copied it.
- It's identical.

279
00:18:12,030 --> 00:18:14,230
Choi Yu Na...
Isn't she the team leader?

280
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,930
She did this seven years ago?

281
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,300
- Isn't that stealing?
- And she's a team leader now.

282
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,800
What's that?

283
00:18:20,940 --> 00:18:22,910
- Seven years ago?
- She won the grand prize with that.

284
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,740
How shameless can she be?

285
00:18:28,010 --> 00:18:29,550
Just look at her.

286
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,220
(Choi Yu Na, the Design Thief!)

287
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:40,920
It's all lies. I'm being framed.

288
00:18:43,290 --> 00:18:44,630
Everyone's talking about it...

289
00:18:44,630 --> 00:18:47,360
on the company message board
and anonymous forums.

290
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:50,370
Ms. Choi, did you really
win the competition...

291
00:18:50,370 --> 00:18:52,040
with someone else's design?

292
00:18:54,100 --> 00:18:55,340
I told you I didn't.

293
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,870
Right, of course not.

294
00:18:57,470 --> 00:19:00,110
How could you study abroad
and earn a special position...

295
00:19:00,180 --> 00:19:01,450
off someone else's design?

296
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:04,780
No decent person's conscience
would allow that.

297
00:19:05,380 --> 00:19:08,520
Maybe she has no conscience
or she just isn't decent.

298
00:19:19,260 --> 00:19:20,300
Park Min Jun.

299
00:19:22,170 --> 00:19:23,670
You really want to take this
all the way?

300
00:19:39,980 --> 00:19:43,320
She threatened my Hyun Jun...

301
00:19:44,620 --> 00:19:45,720
and tormented him.

302
00:19:46,390 --> 00:19:48,460
Talk about a scandalous past.

303
00:19:49,990 --> 00:19:52,100
Go ahead and tear them down all day.

304
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:54,830
I'll keep putting them back up
until you give up.

305
00:19:55,600 --> 00:19:56,830
You see,

306
00:19:58,270 --> 00:20:01,570
I still have 100 posters left.

307
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:08,580
(Choi Yu Na, the Design Thief!)

308
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:12,350
(Choi Yu Na, the Design Thief!)

309
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:14,020
(Head of Division 1, Park Min Jun)

310
00:20:15,950 --> 00:20:17,790
The chairman ordered you
to back down.

311
00:20:18,090 --> 00:20:21,220
Why are you still making an issue
out of my design?

312
00:20:22,060 --> 00:20:24,900
The posters in the company lobby,
the posts you spread online...

313
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:26,830
Get rid of all of it.

314
00:20:27,530 --> 00:20:31,400
If it bothers you so much,
go ask my father for help.

315
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:36,140
If this keeps happening
over and over,

316
00:20:36,370 --> 00:20:38,810
public opinion will turn
against you, and my father...

317
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:40,580
will get tired of you.

318
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:42,410
Then,

319
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,880
he'll abandon you in the end.

320
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:46,280
What?

321
00:20:53,920 --> 00:20:54,990
I told you...

322
00:20:55,490 --> 00:20:57,960
I'd make my father abandon you.

323
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:00,660
From now on,
wherever there's a crowd,

324
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:02,430
your crimes will be put on display.

325
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,040
Once you're branded
the nation's plagiarist,

326
00:21:05,470 --> 00:21:08,270
do you think my father
will still stand by you?

327
00:21:10,170 --> 00:21:12,810
Let's see how well you hold up.

328
00:21:19,520 --> 00:21:22,320
What? The nation's plagiarist?

329
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:25,020
Give me a break.

330
00:21:26,190 --> 00:21:28,430
I have Park Hyun Jun and Oh Jung Ran
in the palm of my hand.

331
00:21:29,230 --> 00:21:30,930
You think I'll go down that easily?

332
00:21:32,030 --> 00:21:34,030
Before you ruin everything,

333
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:36,730
I'll do whatever it takes
to save myself,

334
00:21:38,640 --> 00:21:40,770
even if it means marrying
into the Adele family.

335
00:21:47,610 --> 00:21:51,250
Women are a dime a dozen,
but there's only one Adele Group.

336
00:21:52,520 --> 00:21:54,420
You said you didn't want to live
as a chauffeur's son.

337
00:21:54,950 --> 00:21:56,790
You want to live
as Park Tae Ho's son.

338
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:58,790
Then you have to take this chance.

339
00:21:58,790 --> 00:22:00,690
For Chloe's sake,

340
00:22:01,930 --> 00:22:04,530
I wanted to keep living
as Park Tae Ho's son.

341
00:22:06,030 --> 00:22:08,470
- It means nothing without her.
- Fine.

342
00:22:09,230 --> 00:22:11,770
If love were all that mattered
to Chloe too,

343
00:22:12,040 --> 00:22:13,040
then I'd approve.

344
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:16,570
But she's driven by greed, not love.

345
00:22:17,340 --> 00:22:18,810
Thinking you couldn't help her,

346
00:22:18,810 --> 00:22:20,840
she plotted
with Kim Myung Hui instead.

347
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,450
That got her kicked out.

348
00:22:23,450 --> 00:22:24,780
There was no plotting!

349
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:30,120
Don't make this any harder for me.
Please just leave me alone.

350
00:22:32,320 --> 00:22:33,360
Think again.

351
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:36,430
Betting your whole life on Chloe?

352
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:38,530
That's a stupid thing to do.

353
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:42,300
Depending on other people
is dangerous and pointless.

354
00:22:45,940 --> 00:22:47,300
Hyun Jun, wait!

355
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:57,610
Thinking you couldn't help her,

356
00:22:57,610 --> 00:22:59,820
she plotted
with Kim Myung Hui instead.

357
00:23:05,290 --> 00:23:06,820
Are you really...

358
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:11,500
plotting something with her
behind my back?

359
00:23:13,230 --> 00:23:15,130
What exactly are you trying to do?

360
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,000
Don't tell me...

361
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:25,480
you want to go back to Min Jun?

362
00:23:27,840 --> 00:23:29,050
Let's talk for a second.

363
00:23:40,490 --> 00:23:41,530
The vice president position.

364
00:23:42,590 --> 00:23:43,630
What are you going to do about it?

365
00:23:44,930 --> 00:23:48,170
Are you asking if I'm going
to break up with Jin Ju...

366
00:23:49,230 --> 00:23:50,230
like our father said?

367
00:23:55,210 --> 00:23:58,180
How about you listen
to our father this time?

368
00:24:00,810 --> 00:24:01,810
What?

369
00:24:02,010 --> 00:24:03,750
To help Jin Ju get her revenge,

370
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:05,620
becoming the heir has to come first.

371
00:24:06,320 --> 00:24:08,050
You've been given that chance.

372
00:24:08,750 --> 00:24:10,720
Shouldn't you take control
of Adele first,

373
00:24:11,020 --> 00:24:14,390
then find a way
to hand it over to Jin Ju?

374
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,460
To help Jin Ju get her revenge?

375
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:22,530
It's probably for your sake.

376
00:24:23,170 --> 00:24:25,040
You're just hoping Jin Ju and I
will break up over this,

377
00:24:26,700 --> 00:24:27,700
aren't you?

378
00:24:28,770 --> 00:24:30,040
I love Jin Ju,

379
00:24:31,170 --> 00:24:34,910
but I've let go of my desire
to have her for myself.

380
00:24:36,480 --> 00:24:40,450
All I want is to help her
get her revenge, no matter what.

381
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,290
If you truly love her,

382
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,820
put aside what you want...

383
00:24:47,590 --> 00:24:50,660
and think about
what's truly best for her.

384
00:25:04,040 --> 00:25:05,080
(Bionecos DNA Analysis Center)

385
00:25:09,050 --> 00:25:10,550
You got the test results, right?

386
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:13,580
It's Oh Jung Ran's blood, isn't it?

387
00:25:14,520 --> 00:25:16,350
I haven't opened it yet.

388
00:25:17,290 --> 00:25:19,620
I thought you should be
the first one to see it.

389
00:25:20,290 --> 00:25:21,290
Take a look.

390
00:25:31,300 --> 00:25:32,670
(DNA Analysis Report)

391
00:25:34,170 --> 00:25:35,640
(The DNA from the bloodstain...)

392
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:37,840
(does not match either
Oh Jung Ran or Song Geun Tae.)

393
00:25:38,510 --> 00:25:39,580
This can't be right.

394
00:25:40,580 --> 00:25:41,580
What is it?

395
00:25:41,580 --> 00:25:43,010
There's a problem with the results.

396
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:44,310
What?

397
00:25:49,150 --> 00:25:50,150
Dan Hui...

398
00:25:51,420 --> 00:25:53,390
What's wrong? Is there a problem?

399
00:25:54,090 --> 00:25:55,090
How could this be?

400
00:25:56,290 --> 00:25:59,130
Does this mean Oh Jung Ran
didn't kill my sister?

401
00:26:00,930 --> 00:26:02,030
What are you saying?

402
00:26:02,330 --> 00:26:04,330
No, this is impossible.

403
00:26:06,870 --> 00:26:08,570
Dan Hui!

404
00:26:23,420 --> 00:26:26,520
Why is Hyun Jun so obsessed
with Chloe?

405
00:26:28,860 --> 00:26:30,990
(Bit Life President, Oh Jung Ran)

406
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:35,630
To become the heir,
he needs to leave Chloe.

407
00:26:36,330 --> 00:26:37,330
Oh Jung Ran.

408
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:40,840
What is this?

409
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:42,370
That day, 30 years ago.

410
00:26:43,010 --> 00:26:44,870
What? 30 years ago?

411
00:26:45,010 --> 00:26:48,180
The day you tried to kill me!

412
00:26:49,350 --> 00:26:51,450
Why did you barge in here...

413
00:26:51,650 --> 00:26:53,350
and suddenly start talking
about that day?

414
00:26:54,450 --> 00:26:55,790
Because I remember now.

415
00:26:56,720 --> 00:26:58,590
I remember that day
from 30 years ago.

416
00:26:59,020 --> 00:27:00,020
What?

417
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,260
Are you...

418
00:27:04,090 --> 00:27:05,900
Mr. Park Tae Ho,
the president of Adele?

419
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,160
Please, help me.

420
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:09,870
I don't remember anything.

421
00:27:10,570 --> 00:27:14,070
That's right.
You said you'd lost your memory.

422
00:27:14,600 --> 00:27:17,470
And now you're saying your memory
came back after 30 years?

423
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:19,610
That's right, Oh Jung Ran. You...

424
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:22,010
You tried to strangle me to death.

425
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:23,580
What are you talking about?

426
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:26,180
Admit it! You strangled me.

427
00:27:27,350 --> 00:27:30,850
So what if I strangled you?
You survived just fine, didn't you?

428
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,460
So because I didn't die, it's fine?

429
00:27:34,490 --> 00:27:36,030
You're a murderer.

430
00:27:36,360 --> 00:27:38,600
That's right,
I should have killed you.

431
00:27:39,000 --> 00:27:41,530
I should've made sure
to finish the job that day.

432
00:27:42,430 --> 00:27:44,670
If I'd known
I'd be tormented for 30 years,

433
00:27:45,170 --> 00:27:47,270
I would've killed you
100 times over.

434
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:49,010
For 30 years,

435
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:52,710
you haven't felt
a single bit of remorse or regret.

436
00:27:53,380 --> 00:27:55,780
You even tried to kill Min Jun.

437
00:27:55,850 --> 00:27:58,150
You, Oh Jung Ran, ruined my life!

438
00:27:59,050 --> 00:28:02,650
So just admit it was you. Admit it!

439
00:28:03,550 --> 00:28:05,390
Admit that you're the one
who strangled me.

440
00:28:05,820 --> 00:28:09,560
Have you completely lost your mind?
Should I finish you off right now?

441
00:28:10,360 --> 00:28:14,730
- Oh Jung Ran!
- Ms. Kim, please.

442
00:28:14,730 --> 00:28:16,930
Oh Jung Ran, tell me the truth.

443
00:28:17,770 --> 00:28:21,300
- Ms. Kim, please don't do this.
- Let me go!

444
00:28:21,500 --> 00:28:22,610
Oh Jung Ran!

445
00:28:25,140 --> 00:28:27,310
She barges in here bringing up
something from 30 years ago?

446
00:28:27,640 --> 00:28:28,650
That I tried to strangle her?

447
00:28:29,850 --> 00:28:32,780
Did getting kicked out
finally drive her crazy?

448
00:28:34,450 --> 00:28:35,450
Darn.

449
00:28:38,290 --> 00:28:39,820
It has to be Oh Jung Ran.

450
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:42,060
Yoon Jung, you saw it too.

451
00:28:42,390 --> 00:28:44,160
I'm certain it was
Oh Jung Ran that day.

452
00:28:56,540 --> 00:28:57,770
Amnesia, my foot.

453
00:28:58,540 --> 00:29:01,080
See?
This wretch remembers everything!

454
00:29:02,280 --> 00:29:04,950
How are you still alive?

455
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:07,720
What are you trying to pull,
crawling back here?

456
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:12,560
She even admitted to trying
to kill me. We weren't wrong.

457
00:29:13,090 --> 00:29:15,060
I know. It was her for sure.

458
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:19,100
But there could be something
we're missing.

459
00:29:19,800 --> 00:29:21,970
Maybe someone else put her up to it,

460
00:29:22,570 --> 00:29:24,930
or maybe someone we don't know
was involved.

461
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,870
Someone we don't know?

462
00:29:29,970 --> 00:29:32,580
Yes, so just calm down,

463
00:29:32,910 --> 00:29:34,580
and let's figure out
what's going on.

464
00:29:36,610 --> 00:29:37,610
Okay?

465
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:44,350
But what if...
What if it wasn't Oh Jung Ran?

466
00:29:45,320 --> 00:29:47,590
What did Dan Hui
sacrifice her life for?

467
00:30:04,540 --> 00:30:06,140
You scared me.

468
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:09,180
Why are you in my room,
sitting there like a ghost?

469
00:30:17,990 --> 00:30:21,060
Seriously,
what's been up with you all day?

470
00:30:21,690 --> 00:30:22,960
It was definitely you.

471
00:30:23,460 --> 00:30:24,830
That day, 30 years ago.

472
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:29,470
Oh Jung Ran, you strangled me.

473
00:30:30,800 --> 00:30:33,440
You even confessed to Chairman Park
that you tried to kill me.

474
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:37,870
You took that poison
and came out just fine.

475
00:30:39,810 --> 00:30:40,810
Poison?

476
00:30:44,080 --> 00:30:46,350
So you had someone else do it?

477
00:30:47,080 --> 00:30:49,190
You drugged me until I passed out...

478
00:30:49,850 --> 00:30:51,420
and then you strangled me?

479
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:54,220
Why are you so fixated
on being strangled?

480
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:57,430
If I'd known,
I would've used a stronger,

481
00:30:57,490 --> 00:30:59,030
more effective drug back then.

482
00:30:59,830 --> 00:31:02,930
So you didn't actually strangle me?

483
00:31:04,400 --> 00:31:05,600
You just drugged me?

484
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:10,940
Stop bothering me
and go see a doctor.

485
00:31:11,340 --> 00:31:13,240
It sounds like
your memory hasn't come back.

486
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,580
You're just mixing things up.

487
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:30,860
If Oh Jung Ran drugged you,
what does that mean?

488
00:31:31,530 --> 00:31:33,030
Myung Hui definitely had...

489
00:31:33,660 --> 00:31:35,270
strangulation marks on her neck.

490
00:31:36,900 --> 00:31:39,270
How can Oh Jung Ran
not be the killer?

491
00:31:40,300 --> 00:31:41,300
Yoon Jung.

492
00:31:42,370 --> 00:31:43,510
What do I do now?

493
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,580
For the last 30 years,

494
00:31:47,380 --> 00:31:49,980
I've been holding on
just to get revenge on Oh Jung Ran.

495
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:55,450
I gave up my identity
and lived as my sister,

496
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:57,720
enduring every kind of humiliation.

497
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,960
But...

498
00:32:02,030 --> 00:32:04,390
if she isn't the one
who killed my sister...

499
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:10,370
What are you talking about?

500
00:32:24,280 --> 00:32:25,780
Who killed whom?

501
00:32:25,780 --> 00:32:27,450
And what do you mean
you lived as your sister?

502
00:32:28,450 --> 00:32:30,350
What's all of this about?

503
00:33:11,030 --> 00:33:13,000
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
